    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >测试你的专注力和协调性</h2><br>Urban Flow 游戏旨在确保汽车在城市中的行驶安全。这正是你需要发挥作用之处——需妥善控制交通信号灯，以确保没有事故或交通延误。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235340/extras/935ae4c7710c20a5e5429f4d18d72f40.poster.avif?t=1704295118\" width=640 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235340/extras/935ae4c7710c20a5e5429f4d18d72f40.webm?t=1704295118\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235340/extras/935ae4c7710c20a5e5429f4d18d72f40.mp4?t=1704295118\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >保障城市安全</h2><br>保持汽车在完美和谐的路况中运行，避免碰撞和堵塞，确保一切运行顺利。城市的街道由你来调控，要确保每个人都能准时到达目的地。游戏设有超过 100 个级别，每个级别都有繁忙的十字路口。 <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235340/extras/43a10c319942b8827bf5602511f22e2b.poster.avif?t=1704295118\" width=640 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235340/extras/43a10c319942b8827bf5602511f22e2b.webm?t=1704295118\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235340/extras/43a10c319942b8827bf5602511f22e2b.mp4?t=1704295118\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >确保平稳行驶</h2><br>探索充满活力的城市，汽车、公交车和卡车不断穿梭，并探索不断提升挑战性的游戏级别。运用你的智慧在复杂的十字路口进行导航，避免事故，同时管理多条车道的交通。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235340/extras/7e0cee548c78a589073bac1e7f8525f2.poster.avif?t=1704295118\" width=640 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235340/extras/7e0cee548c78a589073bac1e7f8525f2.webm?t=1704295118\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235340/extras/7e0cee548c78a589073bac1e7f8525f2.mp4?t=1704295118\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >召集你的朋友和家人</h2><br>在本地合作模式中，最多可与四名玩家一起进行游戏。Urban Flow 简单易学，操作直观，是能与亲朋好友同享的完美游戏，无论老少，都能乐在其中。来吧，一起体验管理交通流量的乐趣！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235340/extras/c800c43888ff678b7fd2be82e53944f8.avif?t=1704295118\" width=620 height=194 /></span>",
